4.5.11
  13-07-17
  Improvements
  * #i0023: Flexform: All fields: excluded is set from 1 to 0
  * #i0022: BrowserMaps: oxMap.Render_1.3.07.js is added
  * #i0021: BrowserMaps: CSS .tx-browser-pi1 .mapview-content: padding: 1em; moves to padding: 1em 0;
