  * #i0019: BrowserMaps: cat devider
  * #i0017: BrowserMaps: Constant Editor
            plugin.tx_browser_pi1.map.marker.position.* moves to plugin.tx_browser_pi1.map.icon.listNum.*
  Bugfix
  * #50222: Record Browser is broken
            * CSS: #record-browser is moved to .indexBrowser
            * HTML: id of ul contains uid of the current plugin
            * tx_browser_pi1-0.0.5.js is moved to tx_browser_pi1-0.0.6.js
            Effected files:
            * pi1
              * class.tx_browser_pi1_javascript.php
              * class.tx_browser_pi1_navi_recordbrowser.php
            * res/html/default.css
            * static/setup.txt
  * #50214: Fix core error prompts
            * pi1
              * class.tx_browser_pi1_filter_4x.php line 1320: strpos() expects parameter 1 to be string, array given
              * class.tx_browser_pi1_sql_functions_3x.php line 1090: trim() expects parameter 1 to be string, array given
              * class.tx_browser_pi1_views.php line 894: in_array() expects parameter 2 to be array, null given
              * class.tx_browser_pi1_views.php line 943: in_array() expects parameter 2 to be array, null given
              * class.tx_browser_pi1_views.php line 998: in_array() expects parameter 2 to be array, null given   
  * #50195: mysql_real_escape_string: Bug in case of no MySQL connection
  * #i0022: jQuery UI labels in the flexform
            Effected files:
            * pi1/class.tx_browser_pi1_backend.php
  * #i0018: htmlentities in BrowserMaps popup

