  * #47700: SQL functions 3.x: orderBy evaluation is unproper in case of aliases
            Effected files:
            * pi1
              * class.tx_browser_pi1_sql_manual.php
              * class.tx_browser_pi1_sql_functions_3x.php
  * #47680: Engine 4.x query building: doesn't respect SQL manual mode
            class.tx_browser_pi1_sql_manual_3x.php -> class.tx_browser_pi1_sql_manual.php
            Effected files:
            * pi1
              * class.tx_browser_pi1.php
              * class.tx_browser_pi1_sql_init.php
