              * class.tx_browser_pi1_viewlist.php
              * class.tx_browser_pi1_viewlist_3x.php
  * #47679: tmplRowIsExtraUidField( ) is unporper in SQL manual mode
            Effected file:
            * pi1/class.tx_browser_pi1_template.php
  * #47678: Localisation mode isn't set in manual SQL mode
            Effected file:
            * pi1/class.tx_browser_pi1_sql_manual_3x.php
  * #47089: Filter can cause an unproper value in $arrConsolidate['addedTableFields']

