4.4.0
  130104
  New Features
  * #42788: BrowserMaps will extended for GoogleMaps
            * Moved files
              * default_0.0.9.tmpl    -> default_1.1.01.tmpl
              * OpenLayers_2.10.0     -> OpenLayers_2.12
              * oxMapConfig_0.0.10.js -> oxMapConfig_1.1.01.js
              * oxRenderMap_0.0.10.js -> oxRenderMap_1.1.02.js
            * ID of filter is moved from filter to oxMapFilter
            * TypoScript constants are moved from ... to ...
              * zoomLevel.fixed -> zoomLevel.start
            * TypoScript properties are moved from ... to ...
              * MapControls     -> oxMapConfigMapControls
              * MapMarker       -> oxMapConfigMapMarker
              * MapMarkerInfo   -> oxMapConfigMapMarkerInfo
              * MapMarkerEvent  -> oxMapConfigMapMarkerEvent
              * MapZoomLevels   -> oxMapConfigNumZoomLevels
              * MapZoomWheel    -> oxMapConfigMapZoomWheel
              * OSMConfigCenter -> oxMapConfigCenter
              * OSMConfigZoom   -> oxMapConfigStartLevel
            Effected files:
            * res/js/map/api_1.1.02/*      new
            * static
              * constants.txt
              * setup.txt
            * t3jquery.txt
  Improvement
  * #44318: Workaround bug t3lib_BEfunc::implodeTSParams
  * #44316: Improve performance: substitute_marker_recurs( ) is deprecated. 
            Substitute it with substitute_tablefield_marker( )
            Effected files:
            * pi1
              * class.tx_browser_pi1_wrapper.php
              * class.tx_browser_pi1_filter_4x.php
              * class.tx_browser_pi1_template.php
              * class.tx_browser_pi1_marker.php
              * class.tx_browser_pi1_ttcontainer.php
              * class.tx_browser_pi1_filter_3x.php
  * #44306: Improve jquery loading
            Effected files:
            * pi1
              * class.tx_browser_pi1_javascript.php
  * #44299: t3jquery: respect dontIntegrateOnUID
            Effected files:
            * pi1
              * class.tx_browser_pi1_javascript.php
  * #44300: Update jQuery 1.6.2 -> 1.8.3
            Effected files:
            * res/js/jquery
              * jquery-1.6.2.min.js       removed
              * jquery-1.8.3.min.js       added
            * static
              * setup.txt
              * downgrade/3.9.0/setup.txt
  * #i0000: Removed deprecated files
            Effected files:
            * res/js/map
              * oxMapConfig_0.0.9.js      removed
              * oxRenderMap_0.0.9.js      removed
              * oxRenderMap_0.0.10.js     removed
            * res/js/map/lib
              * OpenLayers                removed
  Bugfix
  * #44313: GPvar is not interpreted in some case: Case is org_npzch
            Cause: GPvar is deprecated. Use GP instead
            Effected files:
            * static
              * setup.txt
              * downgrade/3.9.0/setup.txt
  * #44296: Rotation of modes: $(...).effect is not a function
            Effected files:
            * pi1
              * class.tx_browser_pi1.php
            * t3jquery.txt
  * #44295: Rotation of modes: Content is empty!
            Effected files:
            * jquery.t3browser-0.0.4.js -> jquery.t3browser-0.0.5.js
            * res/js/jquery/plugins/jquery.t3browser/jquery.t3browser-0.0.4.js
            * pi1
              * class.tx_browser_pi1_cal.php
              * class.tx_browser_pi1_viewlist.php
              * static
                * downgrade/3.9.0/setup.txt
                * setup.txt
            * t3jquery.txt

