4.3.0
  121206
  New Features
  * #43854: Workaround: don't use relation twice
            * pi1/class.tx_browser_pi1_sql_auto.php
  * #43808: Reintegration of groupby feature from 3.x to 4.x
  * #43780: New manual: Browser out of the box
            * http://typo3.org/extensions/repository/view/browser_manual_ootb/
  * #43746: Preconfigured view: Out of the box
            Effected files:
            * static/setup.txt
  * #43741: Centralised jQuery UI configuration
            Effected files:
            * pi1/locallang_flexform.xml
            * pi1/class.tx_browser_pi1_flexform.php
            * pi1/flexform_sheet_templating.xml
            * pi1/flexform_sheet_javascript.xml
            * static/setup.txt
  * #43732: Integration of index browser in jQuery UI themes
            Effected files:
            * res/html/default/main.tmpl
  * #43627: TypoScript snippets for HTML templates
            Effected files:
            * pi1/class.tx_browser_pi1_viewlist.php
            * pi1/class.tx_browser_pi1_views.php
            * res/html/default.tmpl
            * res/html/default_ul.tmpl (removed)
            * static/setup.txt
  * #33841: AJAX: optimised JSS code for transparency in IE 8
            Thanks to Renate for publish this feature
            * jquery.t3browser-0.0.3.js -> jquery.t3browser-0.0.4.js
            * tx_browser_pi1_ajax-0.0.4.js -> tx_browser_pi1_ajax-0.0.5.js
            Effected files:
            * res/js/jquery/plugins/jquery.t3browser/jquery.t3browser-0.0.3.js
            * res/js/tx_browser_pi1_ajax-0.0.4.js
  Improvement
  * #43737: Remove button method
            tx_browser_pi1_cleanup_4.1.21.js -> tx_browser_pi1_cleanup_4.2.0.js
            tx_browser_pi1-0.0.4.js -> tx_browser_pi1-0.0.5.js
            Effected files:
            * t3jquery.txt
            * static/setup.txt
            * static/downgrade/3.9.0/setup.txt
            * res/js/jquery/tx_browser_pi1-0.0.4.js
            * res/js/jquery/tx_browser_pi1-0.0.5.js
            * res/js/jquery/tx_browser_pi1_cleanup_4.2.0.js
            * res/js/jquery/tx_browser_pi1_cleanup_4.1.21.js
  Bugfix
  * #43889: consolidation module: foreign table is missing, if andWhere contains table.uid
            Effected files:
            * pi1/class.tx_browser_pi1_typoscript.php
  * #43852: CSV-Export: Is ignored, if you are using several plugins
            Workaround documented. See
            * http://typo3.org/extensions/repository/view/browser_tut_rss_en/
            * http://typo3.org/extensions/repository/view/browser_tut_severalplugins_en/
  * #43803: Category menu: li-tags are missing
            Effected files:
            * static/setup.txt
  * #43778: Filter aren't handled proper in some cases
  * #43692: jQuery isn't loaded in some cases of a treeview
  * #41004: SQL table join: NULL safe comparsion
            Thanks to Christian Weiske for the bug report
            Effected files:
            * pi1/class.tx_browser_pi1_sql_auto_3x.php

